<div class="content-item" id="contribution-6c65aa93-95d1-44f7-9326-ed0b61b7e521">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-6c65aa93-95d1-44f7-9326-ed0b61b7e521">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
