            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-bebc37f6-32b3-4cbc-99a6-00b9d7f2f114" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
