            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3d7f9fe3-8580-4dac-8c2c-0878f239997f">
                Mr. Lloyd George
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3d7f9fe3-8580-4dac-8c2c-0878f239997f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
